ai.seitok.flow.interp

Class Interpreters

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.seitok.flow.interp.Interpreters

  • public class Interpreters
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to maintain the registry and use of Interpreters. Applications can call Interpreters.register(Class, Interpreter) to register their own interpreters.
